    <!-- 
        Demo Data for Party Time Texas Event Planning
        ==============================================
        This demo data creates realistic event planning scenarios for Party Time Texas.
        
        ⚠️ FINANCE/ACCOUNTING SAFETY:
        - All data is read-only and does NOT interfere with accounting/finance models
        - No invoices, payments, or accounting entries are created
        - No payment terms are configured (handled by finance implementation team)
        - No Chart of Accounts modifications
        - Only CRM leads, projects, tasks, and vendor estimates for demonstration
        
        Business Flow Notes:
        - Retainers: 10% or $500 minimum (whichever is greater)
        - Payment: Full before event (individuals) or Net 7/10/15/30 (corporate)
        - Billing: Milestone-based
        - Invoices: Triggered by signed contract and sales order
        - Vendor Payment: Monday following event (standard), some require 50% upfront
    -->
    
